#print all images in ./Solar Panel Detection/runs/detect/train0013
import os
from PIL import Image
from IPython.display import display

current_path = os.getcwd()
path = os.path.join(current_path, 'runs/detect/train0013')
files = os.listdir(path)
for file in files:
  if file.endswith('.jpg') or file.endswith('.png'):
    print(file)
    img_path = os.path.join(path, file)
    try:
        #format all images nicely in jupyter notebook
        display(Image.open(str(img_path)))
        #display(img_path)


    except:
        continue
